    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package is accepted for regulatory submission as a documentation artefact. The overall V&V 40 decision for the CFD model itself remains Not Accepted: all seven assessed credibility factors show achieved levels below required levels, and six factors carry unresolved epistemic gaps at MRL 5. The package is accepted in the sense that it completely characterises the current credibility shortfalls and provides a traceable basis for identifying remediation activities prior to re-submission.",
